data.description: Experience the tranquility of this secluded 3-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom farmhouse nestled on over 3 acres of picturesque land. This enchanting property offers more than just a home; it's a retreat from the hustle and bustle of the world. Inside, you'll discover a flex room perfect for your creative ideas, the cozy ambiance of two fireplaces, an inviting office space, and not one but two master suites on the main living area for ultimate comfort and privacy. Venture downstairs to find a spacious basement waiting for your personal touch. Need space for your hobbies or storage? Look no further than the 900 sq ft barn and the convenience of a 1-car garage. Step outside onto multiple Trex decks and breathe in the fresh country air, taking in the serene views of your new oasis. But that's not all! This property also comes with a charming greenhouse, perfect for nurturing your green thumb, and the added bonus of a shared pond that adds to the overall tranquility of this idyllic country living experience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this farmhouse your own and embrace the charm of country living at its finest. Your dream retreat awaits!
